Cell.Text: You are looking for Arkay's protection while you delve some dank tomb, I take it? | My duties keep me busy in Markarth. I don't know if I can help you.

Node.Caption: DA11VerulusLureBranchTopic: I have need of a priest in my travels.

Cell.Text: [S] G|Treasure, you say? | I suppose the Jarl won't mind if I'm gone for a little while. Lead on.
You know, in the priesthood of Arkay, we have a joke about an empty pocket being better than a full grave.

Node.Caption: DA11VerulusPersuade: There would be treasure to share. (Persuade)

Cell.Text: [S] G|That's no small amount of coin, friend. | I suppose I can come with you for a short venture. Lead on.
I'm just not up for it, sorry. I'd rather stay here, have a glass a wine, and perform my rites to Arkay in peace.
[S] I think you need to calm down before I summon the guards.
G|Don't worry, Arkay's protection is absolute.
G|Let me speak to our guest.
G|Don't be shy. The first cut is yours.
G|This is your initiation into the coven. Go ahead. Have the first bite.
